<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Welcome to Candidate Portal</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
      background-color: #f4f7fa;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
    }

    .container {
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 30px auto;
      background-color: #ffffff;
      border-radius: 10px;
      overflow: hidden;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    }

    .header {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
      padding: 40px 30px;
      text-align: center;
      color: #ffffff;
    }

    .header h1 {
      margin: 0;
      font-size: 28px;
      font-weight: 600;
    }

    .content {
      padding: 40px 30px;
      color: #333333;
      line-height: 1.8;
    }

    .welcome-box {
      background-color: #f8f9ff;
      border-left: 4px solid #667eea;
      padding: 20px;
      margin: 25px 0;
      border-radius: 5px;
    }

    .credential-box {
      background-color: #fff8e1;
      border: 2px dashed #ffa726;
      padding: 20px;
      margin: 25px 0;
      border-radius: 8px;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .credential-box .label {
      font-size: 14px;
      color: #666;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 1px;
      margin-bottom: 8px;
    }

    .credential-box .code {
      font-size: 32px;
      font-weight: bold;
      color: #f57c00;
      font-family: 'Courier New', monospace;
      letter-spacing: 2px;
      margin: 10px 0;
    }

    .info-text {
      font-size: 14px;
      color: #666;
      margin-top: 10px;
    }

    .button {
      display: inline-block;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
      color: #ffffff;
      text-decoration: none;
      padding: 15px 40px;
      border-radius: 50px;
      font-weight: 600;
      margin: 25px 0;
      font-size: 16px;
      transition: transform 0.2s;
    }

    .button:hover {
      transform: translateY(-2px);
    }

    .instructions {
      background-color: #f0f7ff;
      border-radius: 8px;
      padding: 20px;
      margin: 25px 0;
    }

    .instructions h3 {
      margin-top: 0;
      color: #1976d2;
      font-size: 18px;
    }

    .instructions ol {
      margin: 15px 0;
      padding-left: 20px;
    }

    .instructions li {
      margin: 10px 0;
      color: #555;
    }

    .footer {
      background-color: #f8f9fa;
      padding: 30px;
      text-align: center;
      color: #666666;
      font-size: 13px;
      border-top: 1px solid #e0e0e0;
    }

    .footer a {
      color: #667eea;
      text-decoration: none;
    }

    .divider {
      height: 1px;
      background: linear-gradient(to right, transparent, #ddd, transparent);
      margin: 30px 0;
    }

    .highlight {
      color: #667eea;
      font-weight: 600;
    }

    .badge {
      display: inline-block;
      background-color: #4caf50;
      color: white;
      padding: 4px 12px;
      border-radius: 12px;
      font-size: 12px;
      font-weight: 600;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.5px;
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">
      <h1>üéâ Welcome to the Candidate Portal!</h1>
    </div>

    <div class="content">
      <div class="welcome-box">
        <p style="margin:0; font-size: 16px;">
          <strong>Hi {{name}},</strong>
        </p>
        <p style="margin: 10px 0 0 0;">
          Your candidate profile has been created successfully! You now have access to your personal candidate portal.
        </p>
      </div>

      {{#if eventName}}
      <p>
        You've been registered as a candidate for <strong class="highlight">{{eventName}}</strong>.
      </p>
      {{/if}}

      <div class="credential-box">
        <div class="label">Your Candidate Code</div>
        <div class="code">{{candidateCode}}</div>
        <div class="info-text">
          ‚ö†Ô∏è <strong>Keep this code secure</strong> - you'll need it to log into your portal
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="instructions">
        <h3>üìã Getting Started</h3>
        <ol>
          <li><strong>Log in</strong> to your candidate portal using your candidate code</li>
          <li><strong>Complete your profile</strong> with all required information</li>
          <li><strong>Upload media</strong> like photos and campaign materials</li>
          <li><strong>Select categories</strong> you want to contest in</li>
          <li><strong>Submit for review</strong> - our team will approve your profile</li>
        </ol>
      </div>

      <div style="text-align: center;">
        <a href="{{loginUrl}}" class="button">Access Candidate Portal</a>
      </div>

      <div class="divider"></div>

      <p style="font-size: 14px; color: #666;">
        <strong>üí° Important Notes:</strong>
      </p>
      <ul style="font-size: 14px; color: #666; line-height: 1.8;">
        <li>Your profile must be approved before it becomes visible to voters</li>
        <li>Any updates to your profile will require re-approval</li>
        <li>Admin-approved categories cannot be removed by you</li>
        <li>You can update your profile anytime, but changes trigger a review process</li>
      </ul>

      <p style="margin-top: 30px;">
        If you have any questions or need assistance, don't hesitate to reach out to our support team.
      </p>

      <p style="margin-top: 30px; color: #999; font-size: 13px;">
        Best regards,<br>
        <strong>The ITFY E-Voting Team</strong>
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="footer">
      <p>This is an automated email from <strong>ITFY E-Voting Platform</strong></p>
      <p>
        <a href="mailto:support@itfy-evoting.com">Contact Support</a> |
        <a href="{{loginUrl}}">Candidate Portal</a>
      </p>
      <p style="margin-top: 15px; color: #999;">
        ¬© {{formatDate currentYear}} ITFY E-Voting. All rights reserved.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>

</html>
